Ported Jackett Cardigann test fixtures
======================================

The files in this directory are copied byte-for-byte from the Jackett project's
test resources and used here, unmodified, as the offline parity oracle for
harbrr's Cardigann engine:

  html-definition1.yml   <- src/Jackett.Test/Resources/html-definition1.yml
  html-response1.html    <- src/Jackett.Test/Resources/html-response1.html
  json-definition1.yml   <- src/Jackett.Test/Resources/json-definition1.yml
  json-response1.json    <- src/Jackett.Test/Resources/json-response1.json

Source:  https://github.com/Jackett/Jackett
Commit:  b4140c7f8c1f4e1818d5792a6518e7f91861466d
         (the SHA harbrr's vendored definition snapshot is pinned to)
